Berkshire Hathaway HS Pinehurst Realty Group/PH
Premier Real Estate of the Sandhills LLC

data.description: Centered in Pinehurst, this beautiful French Country luxury home sits on a 2.99 acre lot and boasts a saltwater in-ground pool and separate accessory dwelling featuring approx. 988 sq.ft of living area. With just over 4700 sq.ft. of living space in the main house, this impeccably maintained home offers fine finishes and architectural details, inside and out. The exterior delivers a gorgeous brick and stone design. Step through the front door and enter a bright and open home plan. The foyer and formal dining room opens to a large family room with stone, gas log fireplace, and offers beautiful views and access to the outside pool and patio area. This home offers 8 ft. interior doors, crown molding, as well as tray ceilings, coffered-ceiling in the family room, and hardwood floors throughout. The spectacular gourmet kitchen has beautiful cabinetry, granite countertops, large island w/breakfast bar, Bosch stainless steel appliances, Zline, six-burner gas range and stove and large walk-in pantry. A secluded master suite features a spacious bedroom, large walk-in closet, en-suite bath with his and her vanities, walk-in tiled shower with rain-shower head, freestanding soaking tub, and tile flooring. The main level also includes a spacious formal living room/den, two guest bedrooms with a shared bathroom, and a third bedroom with an en-suite bath. The upper level has a large bonus room/bedroom with en-suite bath and walk-in closet, as well as an office nook. This level also houses a large walk-in attic storage space. An oversized three-bay, mini-split conditioned garage offers space for a workshop with custom wood cabinets. Other features include sealed crawl space with dehumidifier and tankless water heater. A 2 BR/1 BA accessory dwelling on the property has a large family room, custom kitchen with granite countertops and separate one stall mini-split conditioned garage. The backyard pool and entertainment area is fenced with wrought iron fence and beautiful landscaping.
